snippet.title: Unleashed Recompiled - Release Trailer
snippet.description:
Unleashed Recompiled is an unofficial PC port of the Xbox 360 version of Sonic Unleashed created through the process of static recompilation.

Download Unleashed Recompiled from GitHub: https://github.com/hedge-dev/UnleashedRecomp

Trailer created by @GPF_SCT.
